---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="one prompt, one video" description="remotion turns video into code. claude code writes the code. under 60 seconds.">
  <div class="space-y-6">
    <div class="font-mono text-xs text-faint mb-4">
      <a href="/writing" class="text-spice hover:underline">writing</a> <span class="text-faint">/</span> remotion-one-prompt
    </div>

    <h1 class="font-display text-3xl font-normal animate-fade-up">one prompt, one video</h1>

    <div class="essay mt-10 animate-fade-up delay-1">
      <p>i made a video with one prompt</p>

      <p class="mt-6 text-dim">not edited it</p>
      <p class="text-dim">not directed it</p>

      <p class="mt-6">wrote a prompt</p>
      <p class="text-spice">got a video</p>

      <hr class="my-12 border-border" />

      <p>remotion turns video into code</p>

      <p class="mt-6 text-dim">react components that render frames</p>

      <p class="mt-6">if you can describe what you want</p>
      <p class="text-gold">a code agent can write it</p>

      <hr class="my-12 border-border" />

      <p>the prompt was one paragraph</p>

      <p class="mt-6 text-water">"30 second video, kinetic typography,</p>
      <p class="text-water">the text is about how this video</p>
      <p class="text-water">was made with one prompt"</p>

      <p class="mt-6 text-spice">meta loop</p>

      <hr class="my-12 border-border" />

      <p>under 60 seconds start to finish</p>

      <p class="mt-6 text-dim">most of that was the render</p>

      <hr class="my-12 border-border" />

      <p>the interesting part isn't the output</p>

      <p class="mt-6 text-crimson">it's what disappeared</p>

      <p class="mt-6 text-dim">storyboarding</p>
      <p class="text-dim">timeline editing</p>
      <p class="text-dim">export settings</p>
      <p class="text-dim">asset management</p>

      <p class="mt-6">gone</p>

      <hr class="my-12 border-border" />

      <p>same pattern keeps showing up</p>

      <p class="mt-6">tools don't add steps</p>
      <p class="text-gold">they delete steps</p>

      <p class="mt-6">what's left is the decision</p>
      <p class="text-spice">and the artifact</p>

      <hr class="my-12 border-border" />

      <p>programmatic video has been around</p>

      <p class="mt-6 text-dim">remotion's been around</p>

      <p class="mt-6">what changed is the bridge</p>

      <p class="mt-6">a code agent that can hold</p>
      <p>the whole composition in context</p>
      <p class="text-gold">and write it from intent</p>

      <hr class="my-12 border-border" />

      <p>tried explaining this to someone</p>

      <p class="mt-6 text-dim">they asked how long it would take to learn remotion</p>

      <p class="mt-6 text-spice">missed the point entirely</p>

      <hr class="my-12 border-border" />

      <p>you don't learn the tool anymore</p>

      <p class="mt-6">you describe what you want</p>
      <p>to something that knows the tool</p>

      <p class="mt-6 text-gold">the skill moved</p>

      <hr class="my-12 border-border" />

      <p>most workflows still have</p>
      <p>15 minutes of ceremony</p>
      <p>around 30 seconds of actual decision</p>

      <p class="mt-6 text-water">find the ones where that ratio is worst</p>

      <p class="mt-6 text-spice">that's where this hits</p>
    </div>

    <!-- The video -->
    <div class="mt-16 flex justify-center animate-fade-up delay-2">
      <video
        src="/videos/remotion-meta.mp4"
        controls
        playsinline
        class="rounded-xl border border-border max-h-[600px]"
        poster=""
      />
    </div>
    <p class="text-center text-faint text-xs font-mono mt-2">the video. one prompt. one render.</p>

    <div class="mt-16 pt-6 border-t border-border">
      <a href="/writing" class="text-spice hover:underline">← back to writing</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .essay p {
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
</style>
